node.text: Today, my best friend @alyssanicanderson is 2 years sober 🍾 (< that’s a highly carbonated bottle of Perrier). Anyone who has the pleasure of knowing Alyssa, whether in person or online, knows that she is the most positive, helpful, driven, capable human being. I’ve been lucky enough to share over 10 years of friendship with her, as well as having lived together for the last few years. Many people told us that living with your friend isn’t a good idea, but in reality it has been one of the absolute best experiences of my life. I’ve gotten to watch someone I love so deeply grow to somehow be even more inspiring, uplifting and supportive. I’ve been able to watch her take on so many new paths and challenges and be fantastic at everything she puts her mind to. And recently, I’ve been able to see her step into the role of World’s Best Auntie ™. Alyssa, seeing you maintain sobriety is so amazing not because you were any less of an incredible individual when you were not sober, but because it’s the first time I have seen you choose to put yourself first every day. And you deserve that 👭

node.text: The hair ritual 😌 Using @playa Violet Brightening Shampoo for the days I’m feeling a bit brassy - I love this one to help tone my hair without over-depositing colour. Following up with @playa Ritual Hair Oil on partially dry hair to provide some hydration 😍 and lastly, after I brush out my curls I use the @playa Endless Summer Spray for texture and volume 🌞  Shop my favorite Playa essentials at @Sephora and Playabeauty.com. Click the link in my bio to use code SAM20 for 20% off of your first purchase at playabeauty.com

APPROACHABLE PODCAST TURNS 2 - I cannot believe how the time has flown by. We can’t tell you how much we appreciate the support because this show means so much to us. 🥲 To celebrate, we are having a 25% off sale on Approachable Merch - link in bio to shop. We also heard your feedback from our first launch and added additional sizes (2X and 3X) - please note the sweaters are technically “men’s cut” as well as oversized, so double check your sizing on the website! Swipe through to read more about our manufacturers. Sale ends May 19th 🤍
